                        <li style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #666; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important;"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:mark@transmacconsult.com" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none;">mark@transmacconsult.com</a></li>
