                        for the rail and commercial vehicle industries.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Malaysia Office</h3>
                    <p><strong>Regional Office</strong></p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><strong>Address:</strong></p>
                    <p>9-2 Jalan Wangsa Delima 2A<br />
                       Seksyen 5 Wangsa Maju<br />
                       Kuala Lumpur 53300</p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><strong>Contact Information:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; margin-left: 0 !important; padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <li style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #666; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important;"><strong>Phone:</strong> +6017 3663 819</li>
                        <li style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #666; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important;"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:mark@transmacconsult.com" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none;">mark@transmacconsult.com</a></li>
                    </ul>

                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        Expanded in 2024, our Malaysia office demonstrates our growth trajectory and regional commitment. 
                        This strategic location enables us to better serve our Malaysian clients and strengthen our presence 
                        in Southeast Asia's growing rail and commercial vehicle markets.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section location-benefits-section" data-scroll-section>
        <div class="container">
            <h2 data-scroll>Why Our Location Matters</h2>
            
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div class="card" data-scroll>
                    <h3>Strategic Hub</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our Singapore headquarters positions us at the heart of Asia's transportation 
                        and infrastructure development, providing easy access to major markets and projects 
                        across the region.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card" data-scroll>
                    <h3>Regional Expertise</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our Malaysia office enables us to serve the ASEAN market effectively, with deep 
                        understanding of regional requirements, regulations, and business practices.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card" data-scroll>
                    <h3>Global Standards</h3>
                    <p>
                        Operating from world-class business environments, we maintain international 
                        standards while delivering locally relevant solutions.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card" data-scroll>
                    <h3>Accessibility</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our strategic locations ensure easy accessibility for clients and enable rapid 
                        deployment of our teams to project sites across the region.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @await Html.PartialAsync("_Footer")
</div>

@await Html.PartialAsync("_ContactButton")
